---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Inkbot Design | Strategic Branding & Web Agency"
	description="Based in Belfast, UK, Inkbot Design is a strategic branding agency led by Creative Director Stuart Crawford, specializing in brand identity and digital growth."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-03-26')}
	heroImage="/images/inkbot-design-team-hero.jpg" 
>
	<div class="about-content">
		<section class="intro-section">
			<h2>Design Built on Strategic Foundations</h2>
			<p>
				At Inkbot Design, we believe that aesthetics without strategy is just decoration. 
				Operating out of Belfast, UK, we are a dedicated team of brand architects, technical SEO specialists, 
				and web developers who partner with ambitious businesses to craft identities that demand attention and drive measurable growth.
			</p>
			<p>
				We bridge the gap between creative visual design and high-performance digital architecture, ensuring your brand doesn't just look exceptional, but functions flawlessly in the modern digital landscape.
			</p>
		</section>

		<hr />

		<section class="leadership-section">
			<h2>Led by Experience</h2>
			<p>
				Under the guidance of Creative Director Stuart Crawford, Inkbot Design has spent years refining a process that removes the guesswork from branding. We don't rely on fleeting design trends. Instead, we root every typography choice, color palette, and line of code in deep market research and user psychology.
			</p>
			<p>
				Our holistic approach means that whether we are developing a custom logo mark, auditing a complex site architecture, or building a high-speed, semantic website, the end goal remains the same: <strong>positioning you as the undisputed leader in your sector.</strong>
			</p>
		</section>

		<hr />

		<section class="core-values">
			<h2>Our Core Principles</h2>
			<div class="values-grid">
				<article class="value-item">
					<h3>1. Purpose-Driven Identity</h3>
					<p>Every brand needs a heartbeat. We dig deep into your core values to extract a narrative that resonates powerfully with your target audience.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="value-item">
					<h3>2. Technical Excellence</h3>
					<p>A beautiful website is useless if it's invisible. We build with modern, lean frameworks, prioritizing semantic SEO, accessibility, and Core Web Vitals from day one.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="value-item">
					<h3>3. Long-Term Partnership</h3>
					<p>We aren't interested in churn-and-burn projects. We build scalable brand assets designed to adapt and grow alongside your business for years to come.</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="cta-inline">
			<p><strong>Ready to redefine your market presence?</strong> <a href="/contact">Get in touch with our team today</a>.</p>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Scoped styling to elevate the typography and layout of the About page */
	.about-content {
		max-width: 100%;
	}

	.intro-section h2, 
	.leadership-section h2, 
	.core-values h2 {
		color: var(--brand-primary-dark, #000d8a);
		margin-top: var(--space-lg, 2rem);
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: var(--space-lg, 2rem);
		margin-top: var(--space-md, 1rem);
	}

	.value-item {
		background-color: var(--surface-color, #f3f4f6);
		padding: var(--space-md, 1.5rem);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md, 8px);
		border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-primary, #2337ff);
	}

	.value-item h3 {
		font-size: var(--step-1, 1.25rem);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.value-item p {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		font-size: 0.95em;
		color: var(--text-muted, #4b5563);
	}

	.cta-inline {
		margin-top: var(--space-xl, 4rem);
		padding: var(--space-md, 1.5rem);
		background: rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.05); /* Very light brand primary */
		border-radius: var(--radius-md, 8px);
		text-align: center;
		font-size: var(--step-1, 1.25rem);
	}

	hr {
		margin: var(--space-xl, 3rem) 0;
		border: none;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color, #e5e7eb);
	}
</style>